@dagmar_fink @lufthansa_de Hallo!
Bitte entschuldige die Umstände aufgrund der Stornierung. Sehr gerne kannst du meine Kollegen:Innen am Flughafen bezüglich einer Bestätigung der Annullierung, sofern du diese für deinen Arbeitgeber brauchst, anfragen. 
Liebe Grüße, Shawn

@shuggiemac1 Hi Hugh,
Thank you for getting in touch. Unfortunately, the vouchers were only applicable for rebookings within a certain time frame during the year 2020. 
Best regards, Shawn

@rebeccaellis10 Hi Rebecca,
our colleagues will reply to you as soon as possible. They are confronted with a high amount of requests at the moment and this makes it difficult for them to keep the usual average responding time. We appreciate your continued patience. 
Best regards, Shawn

@cecieducate Hi Cecilia, 
We are really sorry for all the trouble. Have you tried doing the online claim via our online form on our webpage? Please use the following link https://t.co/1DV32Zxt3X if you haven't yet.
Best regards, Shawn

@romasars Hi Roma,
We are sorry for all the trouble you have experienced. Please let us know how we can assist. 
Best regards, Shawn

@jayphen Hi Jayphen,
We are sorry that you had difficulty contacting us by phone. Due to the current situation, unfortunately, all our channels are overloaded and there may be longer waiting times. Please send us your details via PM, so we can assist you.
Best regards, Shawn

@tinyg210 @lufthansa Hi Anca, 
We are sorry that you had difficulty contacting us by phone. Due to the current situation, unfortunately, all our channels are overloaded and there may be longer waiting times. Is there anything we can assist you with?
Best regards, Shawn

@hijinxxgk Hi there,
Please accept our apology for all the trouble due to the cancelation. Send us the booking code, so we can assist your son further. 
Best regards, Shawn

@lukasminkov Hi there,
Is there anything we can assist you with?
Best regards, Shawn

@ayezutov Hi Alexander,
We are sorry that you had difficulty contacting us by phone. Due to the current situation, unfortunately, all our channels are overloaded and there may be longer waiting times. Is there anything we can assist you with?
Best regards, Shawn

@lukasminkov @united Hi there,
we apologize for all the trouble. Please let us know how we can assist you?
Best regards, Shawn

@anotherDougR (2/2) I can assure you that we are in full commitment for you and we are doing everything so that we can quickly offer you our usual service again.
Please let me know, if we can assist you here.
Best regards, Alessandra

@vongsoftware Hallo,
sofern du mehr über Gepäck auf unseren Charter Flügen wissen möchtest, kannst du über diesen Link https://t.co/v7Tqgw9C4z mehr erfahren. Für weitere Fragen sind wir gerne für dich da. 
Liebe Grüße, Shawn

@ailiasovich Hi Andrei,
Please accept our apology for all the trouble. In order to assist you further, please let us know how we can help you. We would appreciate it, if you could send us your booking code via PM.
Best regards, Shawn

@anorok77 Hi there,
Due to the very high call volume in our Service Center, you may experience longer waiting times.  We are doing our best and my colleagues will reply to your concern as soon as possible. Thank you for your understanding. 
Best regards, Shawn

@KS23765709 Hallo Kathi,
Aufgrund der aktuell starken Auslastung unserer Service Center, kann es momentan zu längeren Wartezeiten kommen. Wir bitten um dein Verständnis. Wie können wir dir an dieser Stelle behilflich sein? 
Liebe Grüße, Shawn

@kevinraabe2 Hi Kevin,
Please accept our apology for all the trouble. In order to claim your lost item please fill-up the online form on the Vienna Airport homepage. You can use the following link https://t.co/fOV6brfkrl 
Best regards, Shawn

@annaclevy1 Hi Anna,
Please send us your booking code, so we can assist you further.
Best regards, Shawn

@mvukotic Hi Marija,
Please send us her booking code, so we can take a closer look. We apologize for all the trouble.
Best regards, Shawn
